---
title: Sweet Chilli Seared Beef Bowl with Garlic Rice & Sesame Veggies
description: Quick-cooking beef strips are the star of this speedy Asian stir-fry. Colourful veggies including snow peas and carrot add goodness plus a generous serve of oyster sauce, lemon juice and sweet chilli sauce combine into a sweet and savoury glaze that everyone will love!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-chilli-seared-beef-bowl-52eb30f4.jpg
